---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="why-roast" id="why-roast">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-image">
        <img src={`${base}/images/dairy-cows.jpg`} alt="Dairy cows feeding at a barn" />
      </div>
      <div class="why-content">
        <p class="section-tag">The Bottom Line</p>
        <h2>Why Roast On-Site?</h2>
        <div class="why-points">
          <div class="why-point">
            <div class="why-number">01</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Keep All Your Dry Matter</h3>
              <p>When you roast at the co-op, you lose 10% or more dry matter. Our on-site service means the only shrink is water. All your dry matter stays in your feed bin.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-point">
            <div class="why-number">02</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Skip the Elevator Penalties</h3>
              <p>Elevators charge 4% shrink per point on beans over 15% moisture, plus drying fees and minimums. At 20% moisture, that's a 20% dock before you even start. Roasting on-site costs a fraction.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-point">
            <div class="why-number">03</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Add Value, Not Cost</h3>
              <p>Dry beans cost $1.00–$1.15 per bushel to roast. Even wet beans at $1.50/bu is far less than elevator shrinks and docks — and you get a value-added roasted soybean.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-point">
            <div class="why-number">04</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Long-Term Storage</h3>
              <p>Roasted soybeans store for years. We've seen 5–6 year old roasted beans fed with no herd performance loss. Most customers roast annually.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-roast {
    padding: 7rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .why-image {
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .why-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    min-height: 500px;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-rust);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .why-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    color: var(--color-earth);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .why-points {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .why-point {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .why-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-wheat-dark);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-wheat-dark);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .why-point h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-earth);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .why-point p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .why-image img {
      min-height: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>
